      • computeChildPaths

        public HashMap<String,Integer> computeChildPaths(int distance,
                                                 Set relationshipType,
                                                 org.obo.datamodel.LinkedObject term)
        Will compute all the term paths from a given term to all its children, irrespective of distance
        Specified by:
        computeChildPaths in interface Parser
        Parameters:
        distance - Distance in arcs between nodes. Set to 1 to begin, will be incremented in recursive method calls
        relationshipType - - a set of possible synonyms for the type of relationship to link the terms (is_a, part_of, develops_from)
        term - The term to scan for a given distance
        Returns:
        A hashmap where the key is a term ID and the value is an Integet repersenting the distance
